{
  "stem": "13623.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We heard the siren again, sort of it's a-- we're-- we're out of range of the bombing and so forth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was close to a morning where we had to get up and Zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] We all went back to work, to whatever work we were assigned to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I continued doing what I did, bringing in food and helping my fellow prisoners, my friends.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] One day, they stopped and frisked us when we came in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we came in-- in-- the kitchen was outside of the camp, so we would have to go out through the gate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And coming back from work we would come back through the gate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we would stand again, Zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would count us again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they would let us go to sleep for the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, I came through the gate, and they frisked us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they found bread, potatoes, whatever I was able to-- I used to put it into my shirt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it used to be-- I used to look like a fat man, loaded with whatever, raw potatoes and bread, whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because I-- I and others that were caught like me did that, we were dismissed from that job.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We couldn't-- they couldn't do-- we couldn't work there anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And we were put into a-- a V1, V2 kommando.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Life is still going on in the camp, the-- the same routine as before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Only one day, they're making us, they're making all-- the whole camp stand at attention, just like at-- at an appell.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they bring out two prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Their hands were tied in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
